                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6774" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1061</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11188 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阳光下的自我救赎：阳光城地产的债务风波</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Self-redemption under the sun: the debt crisis of Yango Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江芷倩，沈艺峰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">厦门大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阳光城集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">房地产企业；流动性危机；债务违约；战略投资者；职业经理人；2022百优案例；重点项目；系列5-3</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Real estate enterprise; Liquidity crisis; Debt default; Strategic investor; Professional manager</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">成立于福建的阳光城，以房地产开发为主业。2012年，公司于深交所上市，由此全面开启全国性的扩张之路。在几任职业经理人的带领下，阳光城通过“高周转、高负债”的打法攻城略地，并在短短几年内由地方中小规模房企一跃成为全国房企13强。不过，“高杠杆、快扩张”的战略也为公司2021年底出现的流动性危机埋下伏笔。业绩变脸、明星经理人出走、战略投资者撤离、控股股东股权被冻、监管机构问询，流动性危机愈演愈烈。本案例通过对阳光城经历的一系列债务风波的探讨，旨在引导学生从企业增长管理角度探索流动性危机出现的原因、了解企业解决流动性问题的应对策略、以及掌握有关控制权相机转移和财务契约等知识点。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Established in 1995, Yango Group (000671.SZ) is a China-based company principally engaged in real estate development. Under the strategy of &quot;high turnover, high leverage&quot;, Yango Group quickly developed from a small and medium-sized real estate operator rooted in Fujian to a national real estate enterprise in China. In 2020, Yango Group achieved annual sales of RMB 218 billion and was ranked Top13 Chinese real estate developer. The high-leverage expansion model, however, foreshadows the later liquidity crisis of the company. In just a few months from the end of 2021 to early 2022, Yango Group experienced a series of negative events including unexpected operating loss, the resign/departure of star CEO and strategic investor, the freezing of controlling shareholders&#39; equity interest, the regulatory inquiry about corporate liquidity and control, and the material default on debt, etc. Focusing on the series of debt disturbances experienced by Yango Group, this case aims to guide students to explore the causes of debt crises from the perspective of enterprise growth management, think about proper corporate responses to debt crises, and grasp financial theories such as the contingent transfer of control rights and financial contracts.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《公司金融》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">可持续增长模型；企业增长管理；家族企业职业经理人化；控制权相机转移；战略投资者；对赌协议债务危机应对策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-11</td>
                            </tr>
